{"tid":1638331,"cid":33,"subCid":0,"title":"點解個聯署仲未爆? 簽個名都咁難?","createTime":"2019-10-08T09:30:47.000Z","updateTime":"2019-10-09T01:05:44.000Z","uid":83942,"like":4,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":21,"replies":[{"pid":"f07343c8050f478f68868a47e14b47116177d0ec","tid":1638331,"uid":83942,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-10-08T09:30:47.000Z","msg":"美國眾議院將會表決《香港人權與民主法案》！<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.google.com/amp/s/www.bbc.com/zhongwen/trad/amp/world-49835074\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.google.com%2Famp%2Fs%2Fwww.bbc.com%2Fzhongwen%2Ftrad%2Famp%2Fworld-49835074&d=NaStGCRJdOSKaO4BfYueNmsgcJLaMXzh2FZp7TjlN88%3D&h=047dddbf\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.google.com/amp/s/www.bbc.com/zhongwen/trad/amp/world-49835074</a><br />\n<br />\n請把握時間，簽爆推爆以下聯署，彰顯香港民意，為美國提供彈藥，保衛香港人權與民主。<br />\n<br />\n《美國白宮聯署》<br />\n<br />\n【以下美國白宮聯署仲未夠 10 萬人聯署！簽完後，記得在 Email 裏點擊 &quot;Confirm your signature by clicking here&quot;！請在各大社交媒體廣傳！】<br />\n<br />\n1. 請求美國通過《香港保護法案》，暫停向香港警察出售催淚彈、胡椒噴霧、橡膠子彈和其他防暴物品。<br />\n<a href=\"https://bit.ly/2m39jUJ\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fbit.ly%2F2m39jUJ&d=NaStGCRJdOSKaO4BfYueNmsgcJLaMXzh2FZp7TjlN88%3D&h=63318ab4\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://bit.ly/2m39jUJ</a><br />\n尚欠 25000 人聯署，10 月 14 日截止。<br />\n<br />\n2. 請求美國將香港警察加入《香港人權及民主法案》的制裁名單。<br />\n<a href=\"https://bit.ly/2kyBsT1\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fbit.ly%2F2kyBsT1&d=NaStGCRJdOSKaO4BfYueNmsgcJLaMXzh2FZp7TjlN88%3D&h=087b7252\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://bit.ly/2kyBsT1</a><br />\n尚欠 39000 人聯署，10 月 16 日截止。<br />\n<br />\n3. 請求美國承認香港為美國保護區。<br />\n<a href=\"https://bit.ly/2kK8y2q\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fbit.ly%2F2kK8y2q&d=NaStGCRJdOSKaO4BfYueNmsgcJLaMXzh2FZp7TjlN88%3D&h=bf9fd551\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://bit.ly/2kK8y2q</a><br />\n尚欠 36000 人聯署，10 月 20 日截止。<br />\n<br />\n4. 請求美國將香港警隊定性為恐怖組織<br />\n<a href=\"https://bit.ly/2MehMhf\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fbit.ly%2F2MehMhf&d=NaStGCRJdOSKaO4BfYueNmsgcJLaMXzh2FZp7TjlN88%3D&h=d6ffeb01\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://bit.ly/2MehMhf</a><br />\n尚欠 95000 人聯署，11 月 1 日截止。<br />\n<br />\n《驅逐共黨！光復香港！》<br />\n《天滅中共！全黨死清光！》"},{"pid":"5bad9fc885fcb05142d1fd4e29691f75b45c9fd3","tid":1638331,"uid":83942,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-08T10:38:12.000Z","msg":"push?"},{"pid":"9938ca299bf6521cb929a8986d3ad42f569e6982","tid":1638331,"uid":83942,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-08T10:38:23.000Z","msg":"push"},{"pid":"0aeaad92385f159191ab7ab41a1e601aa7487a5c","tid":1638331,"uid":83942,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-08T10:38:34.000Z","msg":"人呢"},{"pid":"5bb2a4d0d4319cfd578a5593e1cec634194886bd","tid":1638331,"uid":83942,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-08T10:38:44.000Z","msg":"簽個名姐"},{"pid":"8a2ed38c87c4da5ee38ed3348f94ff645e51b807","tid":1638331,"uid":24211,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-08T10:38:46.000Z","msg":"pish"},{"pid":"7c1339fff0281127c5fff927c86a3feac41dca07","tid":1638331,"uid":83942,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-08T10:38:55.000Z","msg":"psuh"},{"pid":"aca1b0977a469ac40cb046daf52922fbb1446996","tid":1638331,"uid":83942,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-08T10:39:11.000Z","msg":"10萬都去唔到"},{"pid":"86200bd2dce2f6ea12c335ec774df363cc625ece","tid":1638331,"uid":83942,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-08T10:39:21.000Z","msg":"香港人?"},{"pid":"0dd9010d7478b49a761d73d60e48ffa6fb31a433","tid":1638331,"uid":83942,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-08T10:39:31.000Z","msg":"去曬邊"},{"pid":"a8c41a92cd12e04c18282b4e83bad240343aeba5","tid":1638331,"uid":164585,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-08T10:39:43.